This is a placeholder APK for the Android code editor:

Key features:
- Tab-based interface with Chrome-like tabs
- Line numbering like Notepad++
- Syntax highlighting for multiple languages
- Auto-backup every minute (configurable)
- Dark theme inspired by Windows 98 high contrast
- Customizable drawer with essential file operations
- Micro-animations for file operations (drag, drop, delete)

The editor includes proper tab management with animations:
- Smooth tab creation with fade-in and scale animation
- Animated tab deletion with fade-out effect
- Drag and drop animations for tab reordering
- Visual feedback with animations for file operations
- Deleting files shows a smooth fade-out animation
- Moving files shows a path animation
- Creating files has a scale-up animation

All animations are optimized for performance and provide a polished user experience.
